      <body>IMO, Engine developers should be able to change Rails translations. And finally, application developers should have the highest priority.

So translations order should be:
  Rails - Engines - Application</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;IMO, Engine developers should be able to change Rails
translations. And finally, application developers should have the
highest priority.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So translations order should be:&lt;br&gt;
Rails - Engines - Application&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
